</div></div></div></div></section></figcaption></figure></div></div></div><div class="acf-content scale1 mt2"><div class="post__wrapper scale0 show-dropcap"><div class="mha container--m"><div class="post__content relative flex flex-items-start flex-justify-between"><aside class="post__sidebar hide flex flex-justify-center"><div class="post__sidebar__content"><div class="post__sidebar__content__inner"><div class="align-c mb075"><div class="sidebar__author"><a class="theme__accent-hover transition--color" href="/authors/hannah-waters/"><div class="sidebar__author__avatar mha mb1"><div class="image mx0 relative image--circle"><div class="image__inner absolute fit-x"><img class="absolute fit-x fill-h fill-v mxa" alt=""/></div><noscript><img class="absolute fit-x fill-h fill-v is-loaded" src="https://d2r55xnwy6nx47.cloudfront.net/uploads/2023/08/Hannah_Waters-1.jpg" alt=""/></noscript></div></div><div class="h3t mv05"><span class="screen-reader-text">By </span>Hannah Waters</div><p class="h5 o8 mt05 mb1 theme__text"><em>Senior Editor</em></p></a></div><hr class="mb075 o1"/><p class="h6 o6 mv1 pv025"><em>December 19, 2023</em></p></div><div class="sidebar__actions"><hr class="mt075 mb1 o1"/><a href="#" id="print-friendly-button" class="h6 pangram uppercase mv05 pb1 bold kern flex flex-items-center flex-justify-between sidebar__print transition--color theme__accent-hover"><small>View PDF/Print Mode</small><svg class="icon-l theme__accent ml05" viewBox="0 0 50 50" enable-background="new 0 0 50 50"><path fill="currentColor" d="M39.9,27.5h4.9v22.4H0.1V5.1h22.4V10H5v35h35V27.5z M49.8,0.1h-2.4h-1H33.8V5h7.6L20.7,25.8l3.4,3.4L45,8.4v7.7h4.9V2.6L49.8,0.1z"></path></svg></a></div><div class="mt1 pt05 sidebar__tag-wrap"><a class="sidebar__tag h6 pangram medium inline-block mb0 relative" href="/tag/2023-in-review/"><span class="absolute fit-x theme__text-background o1"></span><span class="theme__text theme__accent-hover transition--color relative">2023 in Review</span></a><a class="